	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Merci d'être venu<gender2 m="" f="e" /> m'apporter ça,
<tag a="110" b="3" />!<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Et si tu vois <tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />,<delay8 /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />remercie-<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x10f 0xcd00 0x4 0x6c 0x65 0x4 0x6c 0x61 0x0" /> aussi de ma part, <tag a="110" b="5" />.</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />En tout cas, c'est très gentil
