	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Comme ça, tu pourras manger <tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="4" arg="0x0" /> comme collation.</message>
