	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />?<delay20 /> <anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />De la part <gender4 m="de " f="d'" />⁠<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />, ça me surprend beaucoup.<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x10f 0xcd00 0x4 0x49 0x6c 0x8 0x45 0x6c 0x6c 0x65 0x0" /> veut sûrement s'excuser pour
